<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَشُرِطَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> تَلَفُّظٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَاتِّصَالٌ مُعْتَادٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَنِيَّتُهُ قَبْلَ تَمَامِ مُسْتَثْنًى مِنْهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَيَصِحُّ بِقَلْبٍ مِنْ مُطَلَّقَاتٍ لَا طَلَقَاتٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَأَنْتِ طَالِقٌ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَبْلَ مَوْتِي:</span> تَطْلُقُ فِي الحَالِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَبَعْدَهُ أَوْ مَعَهُ:</span> لَا تَطْلُقُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَفِي هَذَا الشَّهْرِ، أَوِ اليَوْمِ،<span class="c5"> أَوِ السَّنَةِ:</span> تَطْلُقُ فِي الحَالِ،<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ قَالَ:</span> أَرَدْتُ آخِرَ الكُلِّ: قُبِلَ حُكْماً.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَغَداً،<span class="c5"> أَوْ يَوْمَ السَّبْتِ وَنَحْوَهُ:</span> تَطْلُقُ بِأَوَّلِهِ،<span class="c5"> فَلَوْ قَالَ:</span> أَرَدْتُ الآخِرَ؛ لَمْ يُقْبَلْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِذَا مَضَتْ سَنَةٌ فَأَنْتِ طَالِقٌ:</span> تَطَلُقُ بِمُضِيِّ اثْنَيْ عَشَرَ شَهْراً.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ قَالَ:</span> السَّنَةُ؛ فَبِانْسِلَاخِ ذِي الحِجَّةِ. واللهُ أَعْلَمُ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) سقطت من (أ) و (ج) و (د).</p> </div>